  "Description": {
    "English": "Local mineral extract, typically found in large deposits or extracted from common minerals after inspection with an <span class=\"name name-technology\">Analysis Visor</span>.<br><br>Typically found on planets with a <span class=\"name name-technology\">frozen environment</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "当地矿物提取物通常可在大型矿床中发现，或是使用 <span class=\"name name-technology\">分析面甲</span>检查后从常见矿物中提取。<br><br>通常可在具有<span class=\"name name-technology\">严寒环境</span>的星球中发现。",
    "TencentChinese": "当地矿物提取物通常可在大型矿床中发现，或是使用 <span class=\"name name-technology\">分析面甲</span>检查后从常见矿物中提取。<br><br>通常可在具有<span class=\"name name-technology\">严寒环境</span>的星球中发现。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "當地礦物萃取物，常見於大型資源產地，也可用<span class=\"name name-technology\">分析護目鏡</span>探測常見礦物萃取。<br><br>常見於<span class=\"name name-technology\">冰凍環境</span>的星球上。"
  },
